For those who don't know..
1 - Bhanvari Devi lost her mother when she was 6 years old.
2 - She got married at the age of 14
3 - her husband died in 2004(he along with Bhanvari's mother in law played a huge role in Bhanvari's singing career as both were also singers)
4 - she is 45 years old now and is a mother of 9 children

three cheers for the "Folk"Star of India.. divine voice.. way to go madam!! :)
